# üåÄ 3D Maze Game ‚Äì Unity3D

## üìñ Overview

This project is a **3D Maze Game** developed in **Unity3D (C#)** as part of a programming assignment.
The player navigates through a textured 3D maze using standard **first-person shooter (FPS)** controls.
The maze contains a **start point**, an **exit goal**, and an **enemy** that moves independently throughout the maze.

When the player reaches the goal, a message appears indicating **victory**.

