## üëæ Enemy Behavior

* The **enemy** is a 3D animated model with a walking/running animation loop.
* It moves through open maze corridors using a simple **path-following or random-walk AI**.
* When the player resets using the **HOME** key or **gamepad button**, the enemy also returns to its spawn point.

